Document: NoiseTexture2D
Path: godot/classes/class_noisetexture2d.rst
Summary: Defines a 2D noise texture resource for procedural texture generation.

NoiseTexture2D is a subclass of Texture2D that generates a texture procedurally using noise. This is useful for creating various effects like clouds, terrain, or other organic patterns without needing to manually create image assets.

Inherits: Texture2D < Texture < Resource < RefCounted
